{
  "id": "adv_card_yu_06_01",
  "title": "鈴村優 1話 口説いてみせましょか？",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_toffice_noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――バレンタイン前のある日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――One day before Valentine's Day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1733.3333333,
          "startTime": 1.7333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1366.6666667,
          "startTime": 1.3666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "失礼します\n{user}さんにお話があります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Excuse me.\nI have something to talk to you about‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "鈴村さん？　どうかしたのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzumura-san? Is something wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "あー、また鈴村さん言うて、他人行儀やわ～\nうちと{user}さんの仲やんかぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ you're calling me Suzumura-san again. You're too polite.\nAren't we on a first-name basis‚ {user}-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば下の名前で呼ぶ約束だったな\n分かったよ、ゆ……優……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ right. We promised to call each other by our first names.\nGot it‚ Y… Yu…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "んー、まだぎこちないなぁ\nもっとはっきり言ってもらわんと聞こえへんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ it's still a bit awkward.\nI need you to say it more clearly‚ or I won't hear you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "分かったよ、優\n……これでいいか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Got it‚ Yu.\n…Is this okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ……下の名前で呼ぶの、早く慣れて下さいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe… Please get used to calling me by my first name soon.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "今度間違えたら、罰として吐息多めな甘く囁くイケボで\nうちの名前を呼んでもらいますからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you make a mistake next time‚ as a punishment‚\nI'll ask you to whisper sweetly with a deep voice and call my name.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ちょっと聞いてみたいかも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ I kinda want to hear that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "勘弁してくれ……\nそれより俺に用事があるんじゃないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Spare me…\nAnyway‚ don't you have something to discuss with me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "そうです。今日はトリエルの鈴村優ではなく\n瑠依ちゃんの唇守り隊隊長として言わせてもらいます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ today I'm not Yu Suzumura from TRINITYAiLE‚\nbut I'll speak as the Rui-chan's Lip Protection Squad Leader.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.5999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんのお力で\n瑠依ちゃんのCMのキスシーンをなくして下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'd like you to use your power‚ {user}-san‚\nto eliminate the kissing scenes in Rui-chan's CM.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.3999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "俺にそんな権限はないよ\nそれに、まだ諦めてなかったのか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't have the authority to do that.\nBesides‚ haven't you given up on that yet?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.8333323161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "当たり前です。瑠依ちゃんがどこの馬の骨とも\n分からん男とキスするなんて、うちが許しません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course not.\nI won't allow Rui-chan to kiss just any random guy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.5999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんは責任感の強い子やから\nやりたないことでも多少のことなら我慢してしまいます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-chan is a responsible girl‚\nso she might endure things she doesn't want to.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.6999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "せやけど、我慢出来るだけで傷つかない訳やないんよ\n傷ついても「大丈夫」言うて平気な顔をする子なんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But just enduring doesn't mean she won't get hurt.\nEven when she's hurt‚ she'll say‚ \"I'm fine\" with a smile.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.4333323161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "そんなん誰かが守ってあげなあかんやろ？\nせやから、瑠依ちゃんのことは親友のうちが守るんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Someone needs to protect her in those situations‚ right?\nThat's why I‚ her best friend‚ will protect Rui-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.3666610717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "分かった。でもここは俺に任せてくれないか\n瑠依を傷つけるようなことは絶対にしないと約束する",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand. But can you trust me with this?\nI promise I won't do anything to hurt Rui.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.2666610717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんのことは信用してます\nせやけど心配な気持ちは抑えられへんの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I trust you‚ {user}-san.\nBut I can't help feeling worried.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.4666610717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "今も暇さえあればキスを阻止する方法を考えてしもて\nそのうち相手の役者さんを尾行して闇討ちしそうやわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've even thought of ways to prevent kisses whenever I have spare time.\nI might end up tailing the other actor and ambushing them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.799994405,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "頼むから尾行はしないでくれよ？　だが、そうだな……\nそういうことなら一つ頼みを聞いてくれないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please‚ don't tail anyone. But well‚ if that's the case…\nCould you grant me one request?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.7666610717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 152.5333277384
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 152.5333277384
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ここにあるのは、トリエルが歌うバレンタイン楽曲の\n歌詞とデモテープだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What we have here are the lyrics and\ndemo tape for TRINITYAiLE's Valentine's song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.8666610717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "この歌詞を読み込んで\n優なりの解釈を瑠依とすみれに伝えてくれないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Could you read through these lyrics and\nconvey your interpretation to Rui-chan and Sumire-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.2666610717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.9666610717
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "それは構いませんけど、なんでうち一人なん？\n……はは～ん、そういうことですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's alright‚ but why just me?\nHmm‚ I see… So that's how it is.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.3666610717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 172.8666610717
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu016.m4a",
      "text": "うちを忙しくさせて、瑠依ちゃんのこと\n考えさせへんつもりやろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're not planning to keep me busy and\nmake me forget about Rui-chan‚ are you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.5333277384,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu017.m4a",
      "text": "そうはいかへんよ、こんなんでうちが\n瑠依ちゃんのことを忘れる訳ないやんか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It won't work like that.\nI won't forget about Rui-chan because of something like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.4666610717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 185.6333277384
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "もう狙いを見抜かれたか……\nだが、優に依頼した理由はそれだけじゃないぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I already got busted…\nBut my reason for asking Yu isn't just that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.499994405,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
